title: Luncheon Promotes UCF United Way Campaign (University of Central Florida)
text: ( Source : University of Central Florida ) Joanne McCully, RWC , enjoys the diverse foods at Lunch Around the World . At the October 19 'Lunch Around the World,' more than 20 chefs provided dishes or desserts to help UCF reach its campaign goal
